---
---
<section id="innovation" class="pt-32 pb-24 md:py-32 bg-slate-50 relative overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Background Accents -->
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_center,_var(--tw-gradient-stops))] from-brand-100/20 via-transparent to-transparent opacity-60"></div>

    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
            <!-- Left: AI Showcase -->
            <div data-aos="fade-right" class="text-center lg:text-left">
                <div class="flex justify-center lg:justify-start">
                    <span class="text-brand-600 font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-sm bg-brand-50 px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-brand-100">Fitur Unggulan</span>
                </div>
                <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mt-6 leading-tight">
                    Bukan Sekadar Kasir, <br/>
                    <span class="text-brand-600">Jari AI</span> Adalah Otak Bisnis Anda.
                </h2>
                <p class="text-slate-600 mt-6 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
                    Kami mengintegrasikan kecerdasan buatan (AI) langsung ke dalam sistem Anda. Jari AI membantu menganalisis data transaksi yang rumit menjadi rekomendasi stok dan strategi penjualan yang mudah dimengerti.
                </p>

                <div class="mt-10 space-y-8 flex flex-col items-center lg:items-start">
                    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center lg:items-start gap-4">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-white shadow-md flex items-center justify-center text-brand-600 flex-shrink-0">
                            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 10h.01M12 10h.01M16 10h.01M9 16H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v8a2 2 0 01-2 2h-5l-5 5v-5z"></path></svg>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900">AI Chatbot Bisnis</h4>
                            <p class="text-slate-500 max-w-sm mx-auto lg:mx-0">Tanya Jari AI tentang omset hari ini, stok yang menipis, atau produk terlaris lewat chat sederhana.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center lg:items-start gap-4">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-white shadow-md flex items-center justify-center text-brand-600 flex-shrink-0">
                            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"></path></svg>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900">Analisis Prediktif</h4>
                            <p class="text-slate-500 max-w-sm mx-auto lg:mx-0">Dapatkan saran kapan waktu terbaik untuk restock barang berdasarkan tren penjualan historis.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Right: Roadmap & Future Features -->
            <div data-aos="fade-left" class="bg-white p-8 md:p-12 rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-2xl border border-slate-100 relative">
                <div class="absolute -top-4 -right-4 w-24 h-24 bg-brand-500/10 rounded-full blur-2xl"></div>
                
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8 flex items-center gap-3">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6"></path></svg>
                    Roadmap Teknologi
                </h3>

                <div class="space-y-8">
                    <!-- Step 1 -->
                    <div class="relative pl-10 border-l-2 border-brand-100 pb-2">
                        <div class="absolute -left-[11px] top-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-brand-500 border-4 border-white shadow-sm"></div>
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-1">
                             <span class="text-xs font-bold text-brand-600 bg-brand-50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded uppercase">Sudah Tersedia</span>
                        </div>
                        <h5 class="font-bold text-slate-900">Jari AI & Sinkronisasi Offline</h5>
                        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-1">Sistem kasir cerdas yang tetap jalan walau internet mati.</p>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Step 2 -->
                    <div class="relative pl-10 border-l-2 border-brand-100 pb-2">
                        <div class="absolute -left-[11px] top-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-brand-200 border-4 border-white shadow-sm"></div>
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-1">
                             <span class="text-xs font-bold text-blue-600 bg-blue-50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded uppercase">Sedang Dikembangkan</span>
                        </div>
                        <h5 class="font-bold text-slate-900">Manajemen Karyawan & Multi-Cabang</h5>
                        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-1">Atur akses kasir/manager dan pantau performa setiap outlet dari satu dashboard.</p>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Step 3 -->
                    <div class="relative pl-10">
                        <div class="absolute -left-[11px] top-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-slate-200 border-4 border-white shadow-sm"></div>
                         <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-1">
                             <span class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 bg-slate-100 px-2 py-0.5 rounded uppercase">Masa Depan</span>
                        </div>
                        <h5 class="font-bold text-slate-900">Modul Jasa (Laundry & Rental)</h5>
                        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-1">Ekspansi fitur untuk mendukung bisnis berbasis waktu dan timbangan.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="mt-10 pt-8 border-t border-slate-100">
                    <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm italic">"Kami terus berinovasi untuk membantu Anda mengatur bisnis dengan lebih mudah."</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
